@baseUrl = https://localhost:7113

# Before sending these requests, replace ./sample.png with a real local image path.
# Supported formats: JPG, JPEG, PNG, WEBP. Maximum file size: 5 MB.

### Upload template image
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/uploads/templates
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----MemoidBoundary

------MemoidBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./sample.png
------MemoidBoundary--

### Upload custom source image
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/uploads/custom
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----MemoidBoundary

------MemoidBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./sample.png
------MemoidBoundary--

### Upload generated meme image
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/uploads/generated
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----MemoidBoundary

------MemoidBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./sample.png
------MemoidBoundary--

### Upload invalid content type negative test
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/uploads/custom
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----MemoidBoundary

------MemoidBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

< ./sample.txt
------MemoidBoundary--

